OL,3,C2,487 water pollution incidents
OL,4,Crecorded in 2024, say campaigners
OL,6,FWater companies in England recorded
OL,7,F2,487 pollution incidents last year `
OL,8,Fmore than double the target set by the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency, according to
OL,10,Fcampaigners.
OL,12,FFirms were collectively set an
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency target of a 40%
OL,14,Freduction in pollution incidents but
OL,15,Finstead recorded a 30% increase,
OL,16,FSurfers Against Sewage (SAS) said,
OL,17,Fbased on freedom of information data.
OL,19,FThe 2,487 pollution incidents in 2024
OL,20,Fwere the highest in a decade, the
OL,21,Fannual SAS Water Quality Report said.
